title: 11/25/20 DPS-BEST OF
itunes:title: 11/25/20 DPS-BEST OF
description:
On Today's episode of the Dan Patrick Show, DP takes a look at the College Football Playoff Rankings. Why isn't BYU higher? Could they climb the rankings by scheduling another game? We're joined by HoFer Charles Barkley and Packers QB Aaron Rodgers. Plus, Fritzy does his Thanksgiving names, but another Danette steals the show. Happy Thanksgiving!
